  "title": "LLM 省钱大测评！48 块 GH200，首个百亿级参数量实证",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652597724&idx=3&sn=9e1c3a533c3ed56f2772023982580292",
  "date": "2025-05-29 04:46:00",
